801.html|title=OTP Bank Liga Top Goalscorers 2009/10|website=Soccervista.com|accessdate=23 October 2017}}</ref> [[2013\u201314 Nemzeti Bajnoks\u00e1g I|2013\u201314]] (18 goals; shared with [[Attila Simon (footballer, born 1983)|Attila Simon]]),<ref>{{cite web|url =http://www.mlsz.hu/goalshooter/?versenyId=10689|title=OTP Bank Liga G\u00f3ll\u00f6v\u0151lista 2013/14|language=Hungarian}}</ref> [[2014\u201315 Nemzeti Bajnoks\u00e1g I|2014\u201315]] (21 goals)<ref>{{cite web|url =http://www.soccervista.com/topscorer-NB_I-2014_2015-836181.html|title=OTP Bank Liga Top Goalscorers 2014/15|website=Soccervista.com|accessdate=23 October 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Ekstraklasa]] Top scorer: [[2015\u201316 Ekstraklasa|2015\u201316]] (28 goals)\n* [[Polish Cup]] Top scorer: [[2015\u201316 Polish Cup|2015\u201316]] (6 goals)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.90minut.pl/strzelcy.php?id=8073 |title=Strzelcy |language=Polish}}</ref>\n* [[Ekstraklasa]] Player of the Month: August 2015,<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.przegladsportowy.pl/nemanja-nikolic-odebral-statuetke-dla-najlepszego-pilkarza-sierpnia,artykul,603064,1,12684.html|title = Nikoli\u0107 pi\u0142karzem miesi\u0105ca sierpnia Ekstraklasy 2015|language = Polish|access-date = 2015-11-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304042203/http://www.przegladsportowy.pl/nemanja-nikolic-odebral-statuetke-dla-najlepszego-pilkarza-sierpnia,artykul,603064,1,12684.html|archive-date = 2016-03-04|url-status = dead}}</ref> September 2015,<ref>{{cite web|title = PI\u0141KARZ MIESI\u0104CA: NEMANJA NIKOLI\u0106!|url = http://www.ekstraklasa.org/pilkarz-miesiaca-nemanja-nikolic|language=Polish}}</ref> October 2015<ref>{{cite web|title = Hat-trick Nikolicia!|url = http://www.ekstraklasa.org/hat-trick-nikolicia|language=Polish}}</ref>\n* [[Ekstraklasa]] Best Forward: [[2015\u201316 Ekstraklasa|2015\u201316]]<ref name=\"nemzetisport.hu\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nemzetisport.hu/legiosok/legiosok-nikolics-harom-egyeni-dijat-is-besoport-2501699|