hrow|1972]]\n|next = [[Athletics at the 1980 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's javelin throw|1980]]\n}}\n{{AthleticsAt1976SummerOlympics}}\nThe '''[[Javelin throw|Men's Javelin Throw]]''' event at the '''[[Athletics at the 1976 Summer Olympics|1976 Summer Olympics]]''' in [[Montreal|Montreal, Quebec]], [[Canada]], had an entrylist of 23 competitors, with two qualifying groups (23 throwers) before the final (15) took place on Saturday Monday 26, 1976. The top twelve and ties, and all those reaching 79.00 metres advanced to the final. The qualification round was held on Sunday 25, 1976.<ref name=\"SR\">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/1976/ATH/mens-javelin-throw.html |title=Athletics at the 1976 Montreal Summer Games: Men's Javelin Throw |accessdate=18 January 2018 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>\n\n==Medalists==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\" text-align:center; font-size:110%;\" width=\"35%\"\n|- \n|{{OlympicGoldMedalist|[[Mikl\u00f3s N\u00e9meth (athlete)|Mikl\u00f3s N\u00e9meth]]|HUN|1976 Summer}}\n|-\n|{{OlympicSilverMedalist|[[Hannu Siitonen]]|FIN|1976 Summer}}\n|-\n|{{OlympicBronzeMedalist|[[Gheorghe Megelea]]|ROM|1976 Summer}}\n|}\n\n==Abbreviations==\n*''All results shown are in metres''\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\" text-align:center; font-size:110%;\" width=\"35%\"\n|-\n|bgcolor=\"ccffcc\"| '''Q''' || automatic qualification\n|-\n|bgcolor=\"ddffdd\"| '''q''' || qualification by rank\n|-\n|'''DNS''' || did not start\n|-\n|'''NM''' || no mark\n|-\n|'''OR''' || olympic record\n|-\n|'''WR''' || world record\n|-\n|'''AR''' || area record\n|-\n|'''NR''' || national record\n|-\n|'''PB''' || personal best\n|-\n|'''SB''' || season best\n|}\n\n==Records==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\" text-align:center; font-size:110%;\" width=\"95%\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"5\"|Standing records prior to the 1976 Summer Olympics\n|-\n| [[List of world records in athletics|World Record]] || {{flagathlete|[[Klaus Wolfermann]]|FRG}} || '''94.08 m '''|| May 5, 1973 || {{flagicon|FRG}} [[Leverkusen]], [[West Germany]]\n|-\n| [[List of Olympic records in athletics|Olympic Record]] || {{flagathlete|[[Klaus Wolfermann]]|FRG}} || '''90.48 m '''|| September 3, 1972 || {{flagicon|FRG}} [[Munich]], [[West Germany]]\n|}\n\n==Qualification==\n\n===Group A===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\" text-align:center; font-size:110%;\" width=\"95%\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Rank\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Overall\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Athlete\n!colspan=\"3\"|Attempts\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Result\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Note\n|-\n!1\n!2\n!3\n|- style=\"background:#ccffcc;\"\n| 1 || 1||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Seppo Hovinen]]|FIN|1976 Summer}}\n|89.76\n|align=\"center\" |&mdash;\n|align=\"center\" |&mdash;\n|align=\"center\" |'''89.76 m'''||\n|- style=\"background:#ccffcc;\"\n| 2 || 2||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Mikl\u00f3s N\u00e9meth (athlete)|Mikl\u00f3s N\u00e9meth]]|HUN|1976 Summer}}\n|89.28\n|align=\"center\" |&mdash;\n|align=\"center\" |&mdash;\n|align=\"center\" |'''89.28 m'''||\n|- style=\"background:#ccffcc;\"\n| 3 || 6||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Jorma Jaakola]]|FIN|1976 Summer}}\n|83.84\n|align=\"center\" |&mdash;\n|align=\"center\" |&mdash;\n|align=\"center\" |'''83.84 m'''||\n|- style=\"background:#ccffcc;\"\n| 4 || 7||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Piotr Bielczyk]]|POL|1976 Summer}}\n|82.56\n|align=\"center\" |&mdash;\n|align=\"center\" |&mdash; \n|align=\"center\" |'''82.56 m'''||\n|- style=\"background:#ccffcc;\"\n| 5 || 8||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Michael Wessing]]|FRG|1976 Summer}}\n|75.98\n|78.28\n|82.54\n|align=\"center\" |'''82.54 m'''||\n|- style=\"background:#ccffcc;\"\n| 6 || 9||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[Terje Thorslund]]|NOR|1976 Summer}}\n|82.52\n|align=\"center\" |&mdash;\n|align=\"center\" |&mdash;\n|align=\"center\" |'''82.52 m'''||\n|- style=\"background:#ccffcc;\"\n| 7 || 10||align=left| {{flagIOCathlete|[[J\u0101nis L\u016bsis]]|URS|1976 Summer}}\n|82.08\n|align=\"center\" |&mdash;\n|align=\"center\" |&mdash;\n|align=\