nter|\u221214\n|4 strokes\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Jimmy Clark (golfer)|Jimmy Clark]] \n|-\n|align=center|13\n|align=right|Mar 7, [[1965 PGA Tour|1965]]\n|[[Pensacola Open Invitational]]\n|align=right|68-71-65-73=277\n|align=center|\u221211\n|Playoff\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Jack Nicklaus]]\n|-\n|align=center|14\n|align=right|Mar 14, 1965\n|[[Doral Open Invitational]] \n|align=right|65-71-71-67=274\n|align=center|\u221214\n|1 stroke\n|{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Bruce Devlin]]\n|-\n|align=center|15\n|align=right|Feb 6, [[1966 PGA Tour|1966]]\n|[[Bob Hope Desert Classic]]\n|align=right|70-72-68-73-66=349\n|align=center|\u221211\n|Playoff\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Arnold Palmer]]\n|-\n|align=center|16\n|align=right|Mar 27, 1966\n|[[Jacksonville Open Invitational]]\n|align=right|71-65-66-71=273\n|align=center|\u221215\n|1 stroke\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Gay Brewer]]\n|-\n|align=center|17\n|align=right|Apr 3, 1966\n|[[Greater Greensboro Open]] <small>(2)</small>\n|align=right|65-70-71-70=276\n|align=center|\u22128\n|Playoff\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Tom Weiskopf]]\n|-\n|align=center|18\n|align=right|Mar 5, [[1967 PGA Tour|1967]]\n|[[Doral Open Invitational]] <small>(2)</small>\n|align=right|68-71-66-70=275\n|align=center|\u22129\n|1 stroke\n|{{flagicon|ZAF|1928}} [[Harold Henning]], {{flagicon|USA}} [[Art Wall Jr.]]\n|-\n|align=center|19\n|align=right|Dec 13, [[1970 PGA Tour|1970]]\n|[[Bahama Islands Open]]\n|align=right|66-70-68-68=272\n|align=center|\u221216\n|Playoff\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Chris Blocker]]\n|-\n|align=center|20\n|align=right|Jun 4, [[1972 PGA Tour|1972]]\n|[[Kemper Open]]\n|align=right|71-68-68-68=275\n|align=center|\u221213\n|1 stroke\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Lee Trevino]]\n|}\n\n'''PGA Tour playoff record (5\u20135)'''\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:95%;\"\n!No.!!Year!!Tournament!!Opponent!!Result\n|-style=\"background:#D0F0C0;\"\n|align=center|1\n|1956\n|[[Canadian Open (golf)|Canadian Open]]<br>(as an amateur)\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Dow Finsterwald]]\n|Won with par on first 